title: Elemental Jewels v1.0.2
description:
Deep under the Earth's surface there is a secret hidden laboratory...

For the last 20 years a crazy scienist has been working on a powerful energy source based on natural elements. Your mission is to help him by playing with Elemental Jewels!

Classic match-3-hit gameplay powered up with incredible graphics, explosions and many different game modes. 

Play in normal mode, try the classic time attack, start a great adventure in the campaign or simply create your own custom game mode with all the rules you wish!
Please email us if you could help with localizing game to your language.

What's New:

Few minor fixes and upgrades
